会有人愿意接近我，我注定一直是一个人，这是我必然的宿命。 我也真的好想像别人一样活的灿烂而热烈，好好感受生活，这些日子我学业基本摆烂，可是玩得也并不开心，有时候心血来潮一个人逛街旅游或者干脆打一天游戏，之后也只有空虚，感受不到快乐。 现在我的妄想症已经到了挺严重的阶段，连过生日都要幻想出一群不存在的朋友来陪自己，也许我还是渴望能有亲密关系的吧。 真的不知道该怎么办了，可是我也很难接受以后就这样独自烂掉的命运，想请大家给点建议，或者劝劝我。"},"attached_info":"CkkI4bCtpNe6qL4FEAMaCTExNDMxODkyMSDdo7q/BjAAODZAHHITMTg5MTI0NTg5MDQ2MDY5MjU5MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"62 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1744381244.829541","card_id":"Q_1893559105492337659","target":{"id":1893559105492337700,"title":"为什么这个赛季的皇马一遇到硬仗就不行了？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1893559105492337659","type":"question","created":1744239671,"answer_count":21,"follower_count":31,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[18122],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"感觉稍微打强一点的对手就被虐。"},"attached_info":"CkkI4bCtpNe6qL4FEAMaCTExNDQxODMzMyC3+Nu/BjAAOB9AHXITMTg5MzU1OTEwNTQ5MjMzNzY1OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d786b3f161e6246dfa14595bb6ccae40_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]}],"description":{"time":"2025-04-11 22:20:45"}}